      "source": "def manhattan(p1, p2):\n    x1, y1 = p1\n    x2, y2 = p2\n    return abs(x1 - x2) + abs(y1 - y2)\n\n\ndef euclidean(p1, p2):\n    x1, y1 = p1\n    x2, y2 = p2\n    return ((x1 - x2) ** 2 + (y1 - y2) ** 2) ** 0.5",
